Package com.google.gxp.compiler.validate

Class Summary
ConflictingVarNameError An Alert that indicates that a conflicting variable name was found.
DuplicateAttributeError An Alert that indicates that an OutputElement was specified with a duplicate attribute.
DuplicateParameterNameError An Alert that indicates that a template has two parameters with the same name or that a parameter name conflicts with a name being accepted by a bundle.
InterfaceParamHasConstructorError Alert which indicates that a gxp:param attatched to a gxp:interface has a constructor attribute.
InterfaceParamHasDefaultValueError Alert which indicates that a gxp:param attatched to a gxp:interface has a default attribute.
InvalidAttrBundleError Alert which indicates that an invlaid attribute bundle name was specified by gxp:bundles.
MismatchedAttributeValidatorsError Alert which indicates that when an attribute bundle was expanded for an output element there was a mismatch between the validators for a given element.
NumParamsMismatchError ErrorAlert indicating that the number of parameters an interface has does not equal the number of parameters for a template that implements the interface.
ParamConstructorMismatchError ErrorAlert indicating that an interface param required a constructor and the template param didn't provide it.
ParamDefaultMismatchError ErrorAlert indicating that an interface param required a default and the template param didn't provide it.
ParamNameMismatchError ErrorAlert indicating that the Nth parameter of a template does not match the Nth parameter of an interface that the template implements.
ParamTypeMismatchError ErrorAlert indicating that there is a type mismatch between a template and interface parameter.
SchemaMismatchError ErrorAlert indicating that the schma of an Implementable does not match the schema of a template that implements that Implementable
TemplateParamWithHasConstructorError Alert which indicates that a gxp:param attatched to a gxp:template has a has-constructor attribute.
TemplateParamWithHasDefaultError Alert which indicates that a gxp:param attatched to a gxp:interface has a default attribute.
TooManyContentParametersError An Alert that indicates that a template has more than one content parameter.
ValidatedTree The output of Validator.
Validator Validates the tree.
